{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place pistachios into mixing bowl and chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>. Transfer onto a plate and set aside.","Place garlic and mint into mixing bowl and chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add yoghurt, cumin, paprika, salt and pepper and mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside. Rinse mixing bowl.","Place water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma dish into position and weigh pumpkin into it. Add 2 teaspoons of the oil to pumpkin and toss to coat.","Place lamb onto Varoma tray and brush with remaining 2 teaspoons oil. Sprinkle with extra cumin, paprika, salt and pepper to season. Insert Varoma tray with seasoned lamb, secure Varoma lid and steam <nobr>8 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Stir pumpkin and turn lamb cutlets to ensure even cooking. Secure Varoma lid and steam <nobr>6-8 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr> or until lamb is cooked to your liking. Remove Varoma and set aside to cool for approx. 3-5 minutes. Dip 1 side of each cutlet into the reserved yoghurt dressing, then into the reserved chopped pistachios and transfer onto a plate.","Place spinach, capers, tomatoes, avocado and steamed pumpkin into a large bowl and toss to combine. Sprinkle with remaining chopped pistachios, then serve with lamb cutlets and remaining yoghurt dressing."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["50 g shelled unsalted pistachio nuts","1 garlic clove","12 fresh mint leaves","200 g natural yoghurt","¼ tsp ground cumin, plus extra for sprinkling","¼ tsp ground smoked paprika, plus extra for sprinkling","2 pinches salt, plus extra for sprinkling","2 pinches ground black pepper, plus extra for sprinkling","500 g water","400 g pumpkin, peeled and cut into cubes (2 cm)","1 tbsp oil","8 lamb cutlets, trimmed (see Tip)","60 g fresh baby spinach leaves","1 tbsp baby pickled capers","12 cherry tomatoes, cut into halves","1 avocado, flesh only, cut into pieces"]}],"id":"r150486","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-uDblr5fDNCw\/XZQHO1UKUDI\/AAAAAAAAcG0\/sYdfxiq3mZkrDH4DtumMptosx9OCli2fwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_fVBh_BVmJI8UE1vE.png","title":"Lamb cutlets with pumpkin and pistachio salad","publishedAt":"2018-04-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"20.6 g","fat":"29.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"10 g","calories":"1697 kJ \/ 404 kcal"},"usefulItems":"plate, bowl, pastry brush, large bowl","hintsAndTricks":["You can trim the cutlets yourself, but most butchers will do it for you."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","40m","4 portions"]}